                <h1>Customize Your SolidWorks Background: Easy Steps!</h1>
                <p>To change the SolidWorks background, open the software and navigate to the "System Options." Click on "Colors" and you will find options for "Background." Here, you can select different colors or set a specific image as the background. Once you make your choice, hit "OK" to apply the changes for a customized workspace.</p>
